</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 删缓存简单，下次读自然重建
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">延迟双删（进一步优化）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  1. 删缓存
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  2. 更新DB
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  3. 睡眠500ms（等待主从同步）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  4. 再次删缓存</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
